{"tid":931847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水喉匠8樓外牆工作　失足飛墮平台重創","createTime":"2018-12-07T10:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T10:40:02.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"618ce88c9c24204bd6231ae9bd8809737737e294","tid":931847,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/photo/bkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181207180904\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181207180904&h=6b1d5b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名男水喉匠於今午（7日）4時許，在新蒲崗景福街104號一幢工商業大廈「開工」，當時他正在8樓的外牆工作，期間疑跣腳失足飛墮平台，痛極大叫，其中一隻波鞋飛脫，在場工友見狀報案。救護員接報到場，將傷者送院治理，警方正調查意外成因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/photo/bkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001_02b.jpg?20181207180904\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181207%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20181207180904&h=dfe7a785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n救護員不忘將傷者的波鞋一併帶往醫院。（袁以諾攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181207%2Fbkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001.html&d=J2lDsVeHwS0B9dU1HFKLq%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=c5a69926\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181207/bkn-20181207174908358-1207_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bf99200f07208d23dd90fef90f0980aac460afd3","tid":931847,"uid":47954,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:17:05.000Z","msg":"唔戴安全帶抵死喎"},{"pid":"6419d06d2987387bb3e72d8d39b53c0a4d433428","tid":931847,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T10:17:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"580c1